WEBVTT

00:00:00.713 --> 00:00:03.422
Ovako smo putovali 1900.

00:00:03.422 --> 00:00:05.791
Ovo su otvorene kočije.
U njima nema grejanja.

00:00:05.791 --> 00:00:07.420
Nema ni klime.

00:00:07.420 --> 00:00:09.477
Konj ih vuče

00:00:09.477 --> 00:00:11.775
brzinom jednog procenta
brzine zvuka,

00:00:11.775 --> 00:00:13.527
a neravni zemljani put

00:00:13.527 --> 00:00:17.909
pretvara se u blatnjavu močvaru
svaki put kada padne kiša.

00:00:17.909 --> 00:00:20.654
Ovo je boing 707.

00:00:20.654 --> 00:00:22.955
Samo 60 godina kasnije,
on putuje

00:00:22.955 --> 00:00:25.172
brzinom od 80% brzine svetlosti.

00:00:25.172 --> 00:00:27.805
Ni danas ne putujemo brže od toga

00:00:27.805 --> 00:00:30.944
jer komercijalni supersonični letovi